{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-qifeng-006__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-qifeng-006", "source_id": "guofeng-qifeng-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·齊風·006.1", "text_original": "南山崔崔，雄狐綏綏。魯道有蕩，齊子由歸。既曰歸止，曷又懷止！", "text_normalized": "南山崔崔，雄狐綏綏。魯道有蕩，齊子由歸。既曰歸止，曷又懷止！", "notes": "南山 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-qifeng-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-qifeng-006", "source_id": "guofeng-qifeng-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·齊風·006.2", "text_original": "葛屨五兩，冠緌雙止。魯道有蕩，齊子庸止。既曰庸止，曷又從止！", "text_normalized": "葛屨五兩，冠緌雙止。魯道有蕩，齊子庸止。既曰庸止，曷又從止！", "notes": "南山 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-qifeng-006__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-qifeng-006", "source_id": "guofeng-qifeng-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·齊風·006.3", "text_original": "蓺麻如之何？衡從其畝。取妻如之何？必告父母，既曰告止，曷又鞠止！", "text_normalized": "蓺麻如之何？衡從其畝。取妻如之何？必告父母，既曰告止，曷又鞠止！", "notes": "南山 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-qifeng-006__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-qifeng-006", "source_id": "guofeng-qifeng-006__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·齊風·006.4", "text_original": "析薪如之何？匪斧不克。取妻如之何？匪媒不得，既曰得止，曷又極止！", "text_normalized": "析薪如之何？匪斧不克。取妻如之何？匪媒不得，既曰得止，曷又極止！", "notes": "南山 Chinese stanza 4."}
